            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! HTMLWallarper is released under the <strong>MIT License</strong>. You can use it, modify it, distribute it, and even use it commercially. No attribution required, though it's appreciated!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
